subject: Film Club - Fight Club
body:
Hello Bulldogs! For our first meeting of the Winter quarter, we will be watching and reviewing Fight Club. As always, our meetings are free, fun, and open to all Tech students. Be sure to stay after the film to rate it and discuss it with us, and follow along on our Instagram to see our reviews from the past, as well as upcoming reviews for the rest of the year (@latechfilmclub).

What: Fight Club (1999) (2h 19m)
When: Monday, December 9 at 7 pm
Where: Woodard Auditorium

We hope to see you there!
Jackson Dammers
Film Club President
____________________________________
This email is sent through the Louisiana Tech batch email system.
